value:
So Sharena is a princess...just like
Celica... Wait! Forget I said anything!

Hmm. All of a sudden, Celica said
she was heading off to the Temple of
Mila. What happened?

Good job out there today. Here's
a snack! Just think of it as a reward
for all your hard work.

Maybe I ought to change my
hairstyle... Something a little more...
grown up? Whatcha think?

Me? Just taking care of my skin. They
say that moving to a different climate
is rough on you. And they're right!

Oh, $Nu!
I have a message for you.
I'm glad I caught you!

I wonder if it's OK to be so
strong...
Not bad. Not bad at all.

Hmm... More power? This is
exciting!

Hi there! I'm Mae, a mage. Now that
I'm around, everything's gonna be
OK. I know what I'm doing!

$Nu!
Am I glad to see you! Spending time
with you gives me energy.$k$pWhat? I'm already TOO energetic?
So mean! You sound just like Boey.$k$pJust kidding! I know you're joking. I'm
happy that we're close enough to kid
around now.$k$pWe've been fighting for a while now...
I think I get you, at least a little bit.
You're so calm and so kind...$k$pSo, yeah, your little joke surprised
me! It's nice to see this side of you.
Maybe I'll see another one tomorrow!
If you tease me, you've got it coming!
I'll be the one who protects Lady Celica.
Traveling in a big group is a lot of fun!
I'm glad I met you. You're a riot!
